om/image/upload/c_fit,q_60,w_645/35c82a4613d48c87a9a0848ddde8e37d.jpg\"/\u003e\u003c/picture\u003e\u003c/div\u003e\u003cp\u003e\u003cfigcaption\u003eScreenshot: Bethesda / Brandon Morgan / Kotaku\u003c/figcaption\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\u003c/div\u003e\u003cspan data-id=\"35c82a4613d48c87a9a0848ddde8e37d\" data-recommend-id=\"image://35c82a4613d48c87a9a0848ddde8e37d\" data-format=\"jpg\" data-width=\"1920\" data-height=\"1080\" data-lightbox=\"false\" data-alt=\"The Strange Door to The Shivering Isles in Oblivion Remastered.\" data-recommended=\"false\" data-hide=\"false\"\u003e\u003c/span\u003e\u003c/figure\u003e\u003cdiv\u003e\u003cp\u003eWhether you’ve played the original \u003cem\u003eOblivion \u003c/em\u003eor not, chances are you’ve heard tales of the oddities awaiting you in the Shivering Isles. This expansion—the largest one for the open-world RPG—features a land of madness under the unyielding control of Sheogorath. It’s a beautiful world, yet so immensely wrong. But that’s why this DLC is one of the best in the franchise, so no matter how many hours you may have already put into the main story and the main world, you don’t want to miss this expansion.  - Brandon Morgan \u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e\u003cspan\u003e\u003ca data-ga=\"[[\u0026#34;Embedded Url\u0026#34;,\u0026#34;Internal link\u0026#34;,\u0026#34;https://kotaku.com/oblivion-remastered-strange-door-shivering-isles-dlc-1851784242?_gl=1*6351sf*_ga*MTk5MTE1MDYyMi4xNzIyNjAzODYw*_ga_V4QNJTT5L0*czE3NDk4NDQwMzkkbzY0MCRnMSR0MTc0OTg0NzgyMCRqNjAkbDAkaDA.\u0026#34;,{\u0026#34;metric25\u0026#34;:1}]]\" href=\"https://kotaku.com/oblivion-remastered-strange-door-shivering-isles-dlc-1851784242?_gl=1*6351sf*_ga*MTk5MTE1MDYyMi4xNzIyNjAzODYw*_ga_V4QNJTT5L0*czE3NDk4NDQwMzkkbzY0MCRnMSR0MTc0OTg0NzgyMCRqNjAkbDAkaDA.\"\u003eRead More\u003c/a\u003e\u003c/span\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\u003c/div\u003e\u003c/div\u003e\u003cdiv\u003e\u003cfigure id=\"\" data-id=\"ae661b433333f8517504b149e9d593ac\" data-recommend-id=\"image://ae661b433333f8517504b149e9d593ac\" data-format=\"jpg\" data-width=\"1920\" data-height=\"1080\" data-lightbox=\"false\" data-alt=\"Mario sits in a go kart while staring ahead at the track.\" data-recommended=\"false\" data-hide=\"false\" contenteditable=\"false\" draggable=\"false\"\u003e\u003cdiv contenteditable=\"false\" data-alt=\"Mario sits in a go kart while staring ahead at the track.\" data-link-reference=\"\" data-link-target=\"\" data-syndicationrights=\"false\" data-imagerights=\"other-license\" data-hide=\"false\" data-hidecredit=\"false\"\u003e\u003cdiv\u003e\u003cpicture\u003e\u003csource media=\"(max-width: 49.94em)\" type=\"image/jpeg\" srcset=\"https://i.kinja-img.com/image/upload/c_fit,q_60,w_965/ae661b433333f8517504b149e9d593ac.jpg\"/\u003e\u003csource media=\"(min-width: 50em) and (max-width: 63.69em)\" type=\"image/jpeg\" srcset=\"https://i.kinja-img.com/image/upload/c_fit,q_60,w_1315/ae661b433333f8517504b149e9d593ac.jpg\"/\u003e\u003csource media=\"(min-width: 63.75em)\" type=\"image/jpeg\" srcset=\"https://i.kinja-img.com/image/upload/c_fit,q_60,w_1600/ae661b433333f8517504b149e9d593ac.jpg\"/\u003e\u003cimg alt=\"Mario sits in a go kart while staring ahead at the track.\" data-chomp-id=\"ae661b433333f8517504b149e9d593ac\" data-format=\"jpg\" data-height=\"1080\" data-alt=\"Mario sits in a go kart while staring ahead at the track.\" data-anim-src=\"\" src=\"https://i.kinja-img.com/image/upload/c_fit,q_60,w_645/ae661b433333f8517504b149e9d593ac.jpg\"/\u003e\u003c/picture\u003e\u003c/div\u003e\u003cp\u003e\u003cfigcaption\u003eScreenshot: Nintendo\u003c/figcaption\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\u003c/div\u003e\u003cspan data-id=\"ae661b433333f8517504b149e9d593ac\" data-recommend-id=\"image://ae661b433333f8517504b149e9d593ac\" data-format=\"jpg\" data-width=\"1920\" data-height=\"1080\" data-lightbox=\"false\" data-alt=\"Mario sits in a go kart while staring ahead at the track.\" data-recommended=\"false\" data-hide=\"false\"\u003e\u003c/span\u003e\u003c/figure\u003e\u003cdiv\u003e\u003cp\u003eThe\u003cem\u003e Mario Kart \u003c/em\u003efranchise has been entertaining us all for decades—even with sibling fights and fits of rage over losing a race from a blue shell at the last second—but \u003cem\u003eMario Kart World\u003c/em\u003e is the first game to go open world. There hasn’t been a truly new entry in the series since 2014\u0026#39;s \u003cem\u003eMario Kart 8\u003c/em\u003e, so being stoked to dive into this exciting adventure is perfectly reasonable. Equally reasonable, especially given the game’s controversial price tag, is to wonder how long it’ll take to beat and what type of replayability it offers. Let’s talk about it. - Billy Givens \u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e\u003cspan\u003e\u003ca data-ga=\"[[\u0026#34;Embedded Url\u0026#34;,\u0026#34;Internal link\u0026#34;,\u0026#34;https://kotaku.com/mario-kart-world-how-long-to-beat-open-world-campaign-1851784366?_gl=1*10o91ha*_ga*MTk5MTE1MDYyMi4xNzIyNjAzODYw*_ga_V4QNJTT5L0*czE3NDk4NDQwMzkkbzY0MCRnMSR0MTc0OTg0NzgyMCRqNjAkbDAkaDA.\u0026#34;,{\u0026#34;metric25\u0026#34;:1}]]\" href=\"https://kotaku.com/mario-kart-world-how-long-to-beat-open-world-campaign-1851784366?_gl=1*10o91ha*_ga*MTk5MTE1MDYyMi4xNzIyNjAzODYw*_ga_V4QNJTT5L0*czE3NDk4NDQwMzkkbzY0MCRnMSR0MTc0OTg0NzgyMCRqNjAkbDAkaDA.\"\u003eRead More\u003c/a\u003e\u003c/span\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\u003c/div\u003e\u003c/div\u003e\u003cdiv\u003e\u003cfigure id=\"\" data-id=\"6ae9cde5a08a8feed1ab8856ad8b24fa\" data-recommend-id=\"image://6ae9cde5a08a8feed1ab8856ad8b24fa\" data-format=\"gif\" data-width=\"1032\" data-height=\"569\" data-lightbox=\"false\" data-alt=\"A racer drives behind a car throwing coins. \" data-recommended=\"false\" data-hide=\"false\" contenteditable=\"false\" draggable=\"false\"\u003e\u003cdiv contenteditable=\"false\" data-alt=\"A racer drives behind a car throwing coins. \" data-link-reference=\"\" data-link-target=\"\" data-syndicationrights=\"true\" data-imagerights=\"fair-use\" data-hide=\"false\" data-hidec